data.description: HUGE PRICE IMPROVEMENT AND SELLER IS OFFERING $5K to help the potential buyers buy-down their interest rate!  Location is the key of this beautiful home nestled on 0.9 of an acre with 7 producing pecan trees alongside other mature trees!  Less than 20 minutes from San Antonio and less than a mile from downtown Boerne shopping, eateries, and walking trails!  You will fall in love as soon as you pull onto the circular driveway!  Upon entry you find an open floor plan with high ceilings, fresh paint and updated floors, and abundant, natural light throughout.  3 spacious bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a large bonus room upstairs that could easily be used as a fourth bedroom/office! This Texas Hill Country home has the most beautiful rock fireplace! Owners retreat has French doors to the backyard with ample space to create your own oasis and even install a pool!  Separate tub and shower and double vanity sinks. Roof replaced in 2021.  Quiet neighbors and neighborhood, only two owners, and the location is a dream!  This property is spectacular!!
